<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA19">
<l>colliṟ kuṟaiyillaic cūtaṟiyā neñcamē</l>
<l>yelli pakaleṉṉā teppōtun tollaikkaṇ</l>
<l>māttāṉaik kellāmō raivaraiyē māṟāka</l>
<l>kāttāṉaik kāṇṭunī kāṇ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no dearth of words, o heart that does not know the means.</l>
<l>Without telling night from day, all the time look,</l>
<l>you who see the one who protected, differently,</l>
<l>the unique Five against all the great armies, in antiquity.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
